<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>76</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 tóng yī gè de qiú tóng yī gè lán tiān
 tóng yī gè tài yáng yuè liàng hé zhòng xīng tóng yī gè kōng jiān
 xuán zhuǎn de shì jiè mǎn le shén de ēn diǎn
 wǒ men tóng shēng gē chàng shén ài zài rén jiān
 ài de huǒ jù chōng pò bù tóng fū sè yǔ yán
 nán běi dōng xī shǔ shén de rén jǐn jǐn xiāng lián
 zhǔ nǐ shì shén nǐ ài zuì wán quán
 nǐ ài zuì měi lì zhí dào yǒng yuǎn</lyrics>
<title>tóng yī gè de qiú 迦南76</title>
</song>